** NEW PRICE IMPROVEMENT **
** APPRAISAL ON FILE **
** WATERFRONT PROPERTY **
** NEW ROOF 2017 **
** NEW HVAC 2020 **
Welcome to beautiful waterfront property! Enjoy a picturesque view of Florida's marsh nature while watching boats sail by on the navigable waterway, only minutes from the St. Johns River, as you relax on your private 12 x 25 screened lanai, with ceramic tile floors. Serene views seen from family and breakfast rooms, and kitchen through large retractable sliding glass doors. Kitchen features granite counter tops, walk-in pantry and 42' cabinets. Custom lighting, 10 ft. ceilings, crown molding, plantation shutters, marble floors, 3 BEDROOM /3 BATHROOM split bedroom floor plan, family room with fireplace, separate dining room, and front office. BONUS ROOM on 2nd Floor! **BONUS ROOM on the 2nd floor with 3rd full bathroom; great for 4TH BEDROOM, home theatre or teen game room!**
Many closets for additional storage space!

** MATURE TREES AND MARSH ON WATERFRONT BACKYARD **
** ADD your personal touch with a custom dock and let your waterfront lifestyle set sail!

Backyard large enough for a pool. Sprinkler system with irrigation meter. For all boating enthusiasts, this property has deep water access! Come make this home your quiet retreat nestled on .45 acre of pure Florida tranquility!
